  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK714">
<l>oḷiyārmuṉ ṉoḷḷiya rātal veḷiyārmuṉ </l>
<l>vāṉcutai vaṇṇaṅ koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ministers should be lights in the assembly of the enlightned, but assume the pure whiteness of mortar (ignorance) in that of fools.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
